pages.text:
We are a family owned and operated Mexican grill located in bright, sunny Florida! We deliver the best in authentic food made completely from scratch. We opened our Mount Dora location in 2006 and we never looked back! All of our locations have full bar licenses and luncheon specials from Monday to Saturday. We also have beverage specials 7 days a week!
Come to Fiesta Grande Mexican Grill and viva la fiesta!
